  main.container(role='main')
    .jumbotron
      h1 ABOUT
    .container    
        .main-content-wrap
          .figure.nocaption
            a(href='https://www.simoahava.com/images/2014/02/simo.jpg' title='Simo Ahava')
              img.fig-img.lazy.initial.loaded(data-src='https://www.simoahava.com/images/2014/02/simo.jpg#ZgotmplZ' alt='Simo Ahava' src='https://www.simoahava.com/images/2014/02/simo.jpg#ZgotmplZ' data-was-processed='true')
          p
            | Hi, I&rsquo;m 
            strong Simo Ahava
            | . I&rsquo;m partner and co-founder at 
            a(href='https://8-bit-sheep.com/') 8-bit-sheep
            | .
          p
            | I have also been a 
            a(href='https://developers.google.com/experts/people/simo-ahava') Google Developer Expert
