            a(href='https://www.reddit.com/r/GoogleTagManager/') Google Tag Manager&rsquo;s subreddit
            | , in 
            a(href='https://www.measure.chat/') Measure Slack
            | , the 
            a(href='https://www.facebook.com/groups/329145737601165/') Facebook Google Tag Manager community
            | , the official 
            a(href='https://productforums.google.com/forum/#!forum/tag-manager') product forums
            | , and 
            a(href='https://plus.google.com/+SimoAhava') Google+
            |  for as long as it lasts. I also try to 
            a(href='https://www.twitter.com/SimoAhava') use Twitter
