          p
            | In my spare time, I play the ukulele, and I enjoy beer &amp; 
            a(href='https://boardgamegeek.com/user/sahava') board games
            | . I also have a beautiful and wonderful wife, who makes everything worth it, and a son for whom I would drop everything else in a heartbeat.

